{
  "brief": "The guest's Perfect Day on Yas Island — ONE premium page composed from real search results, organized into the chapters of the day. On refinement turns, MERGE: add new finds into the chapter they belong to, add a new chapter only when the day genuinely grows, and never discard what the guest has already engaged with. Reorganize freely; lose nothing. THE ISLAND section reads as ONE continuous argument — thesis, then the shape of the day, then the close — and NO element repeats a fact, venue name, or phrase another element already carries. LENGTH LIMITS ARE PROSE LIMITS: when any text runs over its cap, write a shorter English sentence — NEVER abbreviate, and NEVER substitute foreign or single-character stand-ins for English words.",
  "type": "Box",
  "style": {
    "position": "relative",
    "direction": "column",
    "width": "full",
    "background": "surface.base",
    "textAlign": "start"
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "type": "Button",
      "action": {
        "type": "setValue",
        "values": [
          {
            "key": "defaultState",
            "value": "closed"
          }
        ]
      },
      "style": {
        "flex": "0 0 auto",
        "cursor": "pointer",
        "width": "8",
        "height": "8",
        "radius": "full",
        "background": "surface.base",
        "border": "subtle",
        "shadow": "sm",
        "direction": "row",
        "align": "center",
        "justify": "center",
        "transition": "all 150ms ease",
        "hover": {
          "background": "surface.sunken"
        },
        "position": "absolute",
        "inset": "0 0 auto auto",
        "zIndex": 2,
        "margin": "4"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "Icon",
          "icon": "close",
          "style": {
            "width": "4",
            "height": "4",
            "color": "text.secondary"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "$include": "components/hero"
    },
    {
      "type": "Box",
      "style": {
        "direction": "column",
        "gap": "4",
        "padding": [
          "16",
          "8",
          "0",
          "8"
        ],
        "width": "full",
        "maxWidth": "180",
        "margin": [
          "0",
          "auto"
        ]
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "Text",
          "value": "// THE ISLAND",
          "style": {
            "font": "label",
            "weight": "bold",
            "color": "action.primary"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "Box",
          "style": {
            "direction": "column",
            "gap": "3",
            "maxWidth": "160"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "Text",
              "brief": {
                "description": "THE THESIS — one emotional sentence naming what this day IS for the guest, in feeling words. NO venue or place names here (they come later). Plain English words only — never markdown, never abbreviations or substituted characters; write a shorter sentence instead.",
                "maxLength": 160
              },
              "skeleton": true,
              "bind": {
                "value": "statement"
              },
              "style": {
                "font": "headline.lg",
                "weight": "bold",
                "color": "text.primary",
                "lineHeight": "tight"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "Markdown",
              "brief": {
                "description": "THE SHAPE — one or two sentences walking the arc of the day in order, morning to night. This is the ONLY intro element that names venues: name each chosen venue exactly ONCE in **bold**, no other markdown. Never restate the thesis.",
                "maxLength": 220
              },
              "skeleton": true,
              "bind": {
                "value": "statementDetail"
              },
              "style": {
                "font": "headline.sm",
                "weight": "medium",
                "color": "text.tertiary",
                "lineHeight": "tight"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "Markdown",
          "brief": {
            "description": "THE SELL — exactly TWO short paragraphs separated by a blank line, building excitement for the day laid out below. Paragraph 1 DESCRIBES the experience of living this day — senses, moments, ease — in feeling words. Paragraph 2 UPSELLS: what makes doing it all in one place special, and the invitation to go deeper into the chapters below. NO venue names (the sub-description above already carries them), no markdown besides the paragraph break, and never repeat a fact or phrase from the title or sub-description.",
            "maxLength": 600
          },
          "skeleton": true,
          "bind": {
            "value": "pitch"
          },
          "style": {
            "font": "body.lg",
            "color": "text.secondary",
            "maxWidth": "160"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "Each",
          "brief": {
            "description": "Real figures only, taken verbatim from the gathered content — a count, a time, a distance. NEVER invent or estimate a number; omit this entirely if the content carries no real figures.",
            "minItems": 2,
            "maxItems": 3
          },
          "visibleWhen": "stats",
          "bind": {
            "items": "stats"
          },
          "style": {
            "columns": "3",
            "gap": "6",
            "padding": [
              "7",
              "0",
              "0",
              "0"
            ]
          },
          "template": {
            "type": "Box",
            "style": {
              "direction": "column",
              "gap": "1"
            },
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "Text",
                "brief": {
                  "description": "The figure itself, verbatim from the content — a count, a time, a duration.",
                  "maxLength": 12
                },
                "bind": {
                  "value": "value"
                },
                "style": {
                  "font": "headline.lg",
                  "weight": "extrabold",
                  "color": "text.primary",
                  "lineHeight": "none"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "Text",
                "brief": {
                  "description": "What the figure counts, in a few plain words.",
                  "maxLength": 32
                },
                "bind": {
                  "value": "label"
                },
                "style": {
                  "font": "caption",
                  "color": "text.tertiary"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "Box",
      "style": {
        "direction": "column",
        "gap": "16",
        "padding": [
          "16",
          "8",
          "16",
          "8"
        ],
        "width": "full",
        "maxWidth": "180",
        "margin": [
          "0",
          "auto"
        ]
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "Each",
          "skeleton": true,
          "brief": {
            "description": "The chapters of the day, ordered as the day would be lived, early to late. Place EVERY chosen experience into exactly one chapter it truly belongs to, named in the guest's own language — never a generic label. Prefer variety of kind within a chapter — dining + activity + view, not three restaurants.",
            "minItems": 2,
            "maxItems": 4
          },
          "bind": {
            "items": "collections"
          },
          "style": {
            "direction": "column",
            "gap": "16",
            "width": "full"
          },
          "template": {
            "$include": "components/collection"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "Box",
      "style": {
        "direction": "column",
        "gap": "4",
        "padding": [
          "0",
          "8",
          "16",
          "8"
        ],
        "width": "full",
        "maxWidth": "180",
        "margin": [
          "0",
          "auto"
        ]
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "Text",
          "value": "// THE PICTURES",
          "style": {
            "font": "label",
            "weight": "bold",
            "color": "action.primary"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "Each",
          "skeleton": true,
          "brief": {
            "description": "A closing mosaic of the day — EXACTLY three real images taken from the chosen content items only, never stock, never repeated from the hero. The row holds three tiles: no more, no fewer.",
            "minItems": 3,
            "maxItems": 3
          },
          "bind": {
            "items": "gallery"
          },
          "style": {
            "columns": "3",
            "gap": "3",
            "width": "full"
          },
          "template": {
            "type": "Box",
            "style": {
              "position": "relative",
              "height": "40",
              "width": "full",
              "radius": "2xl",
              "overflow": "hidden"
            },
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "Image",
                "brief": {
                  "description": "One real image from a chosen content item, verbatim URL. Must be a DIRECT IMAGE FILE URL — a photo ending .jpg/.jpeg/.png/.webp (often on static.myconnect.ae) taken verbatim from a search result — NEVER a webpage URL (yasisland.com/en/... pages are not images and render broken)."
                },
                "bind": {
                  "src": "image",
                  "alt": "title"
                },
                "style": {
                  "position": "absolute",
                  "inset": "0",
                  "width": "full",
                  "height": "full",
                  "fit": "cover"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}